Effective Date: 07/06/2025

What Data We Collect

Your Discord ID

Your public username and avatar

XP, coin balance, and interaction history (e.g. daily usage)

Server ID where interactions occurred

Why We Collect It

To manage user profiles (levels, coins)

To enable commands like /daily, /work, /profile, etc.

For moderation and gameplay fairness

Data Storage

All data is stored securely in a MongoDB database.

No personal data (such as email or password) is ever stored.

Sharing of Data

We do not sell or share your data with third parties.

Admins of the bot may access stats for moderation or debugging.

Data Removal

You may request data removal by contacting the bot owner via Discord.

Cookies and Tracking

This bot does not use cookies or tracking outside Discord.

Changes to Policy

We may update this policy. Continued use means you agree to the changes.
